Usage: gui_select [-help] {-point {x y} | -line {x1 y1 x2 y2} | -rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}} [-toggle  | -append  | -next ] [-point {x y} [-next ]]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
-append                 # Append the selection (bool, optional)
-line {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Select by line (point_list, optional)
-next                   # Step to next object under point (bool, optional)
-point {x y}            # Select by point (point, optional)
-rect {x1 y1 x2 y2}     # Select by box (box, optional)
-toggle                 # Toggle the selection (bool, optional)